    <p>Af­ter years of sen­si­ble lit­tle heels and sturdy boots, the ap­petite for show-stop­ping shoes is back – and noth­ing makes a state­ment like the power plat­form.</p>
    <p>It was a key com­po­nent of Ce­line’s sul­try Left Bank chic, while at Rochas, pas­tel-hued ver­sions in vel­vet (right) added to the ro­man­tic flair of the col­lec­tion.</p>
    <p>Mean­while, at Rick Owens and Dries Van Noten, plat­form boots came laden with rock-star glam­our. These shoes are made for stomp­ing.</p>

